## Clarification Questions

1. AC 01.1: For migration — are Allow_Cancel_Direct__c / Allow_Cancel_Booked__c checkboxes still used for permission control (AC 02.3), or does only Cancellation Type control everything now?
2. AC 01.3: Cancellation Deadline field validation — should it reject negative values? What about non-integer input?
3. AC 01.3: "0 to 4 digits" — does this mean max value is 9999 hours? Should there be a maximum validation?
4. AC 02.1: "Current Date > the calculated actual cancellation deadline" — should this be Current Date < deadline (i.e., before deadline) for the button to be enabled?
5. AC 03.4: When participant is removed (Cancel Now), is the participant record deleted or soft-deleted?
6. AC 04.2: No approval/rejection provided — how does a Cancel Requested participant get resolved? Manual status change by staff only?
7. AC 07.1: What exactly is the "Master Participant – Master Staff List"? Is this a related list on Master Event?
8. AC 10.1: For re-booking, is a brand new participant record created, or is the old record reactivated?
9. AC 05.2: The detail field reuses MANAERP__Response_Note__c (255 chars). If the user already entered a "Propose new time" note, is it overwritten?
10. Localization: Should the confirm modal text match exactly the EN/JP strings in the Localization table?

